<p>Nextmedia shall have the right to immediately terminate this Agreement with respect to any user which Nextmedia, in its sole discretion, considers to be unacceptable, or in the event of any breach by you of this Agreement. The provisions of Sections 5, 6, 7, 8 and 9 shall survive termination of this Agreement.</p>
